    "key": "2118299cfc6541d8af74ad242d06cde939a6e1a3cbfa310a3caba8a5d07b770e",
    "original": "\"Thrice times thrice to climb, endurance they did find.\" It is said that when Young Anselm ascended the highest peak of the Higgarian mountain range, he took nine of his worthiest followers with him.",
